{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 70449, "create_time": 1649513238, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "今日欢呼孙大圣，______________。", "timestamp": 1649513238}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 70451, "create_time": 1649513396, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "他们是希望有一个神及其带领的团队把社会的不公之处给消灭了，在现代中国的话语体系里，这个神恰好只能是毛", "timestamp": 1649513396}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 70452, "create_time": 1649513425, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "你咋观察的，网上观察？", "timestamp": 1649513425}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 70454, "create_time": 1649513683, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 3, "text": "共产主义就像现代宗教运动很容易蛊惑人心，煽动仇恨许诺光明“对真理的科学揭示”", "timestamp": 1649513683}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 70464, "create_time": 1649514119, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 4, "text": "现代自由主义从这个角度看也挺像的，煽动仇恨许诺光明，小反贼不就是忠实信徒吗", "timestamp": 1649514119}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 70494, "create_time": 1649515335, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "《好 观 察》🙏😅\n🤮🤮🤮", "timestamp": 1649515335}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 70544, "create_time": 1649518437, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "Re Eve: 《好 阴 阳》🙏😅\n🤮🤮🤮", "timestamp": 1649518437}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 70561, "create_time": 1649519742, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Francis: 《好 回 复》🙏😅\n🤮🤮🤮🔨", "timestamp": 1649519742}], "create_time": 1649513142, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1649519742, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 8, "pid": 25942, "poll": null, "reply": 8, "text": "据我的观察，某些人民常把盼毛归这种话挂在嘴上，其实并不是想要再次大吃饱，大跃进，大互害，他们对那个时代的也大多并没有亲历，他们只是渴望一种全民的魔怔来催眠自己（如果说现在的世界是魔怔的，他们需要的则是另一种更为深刻的魔怔），以此来达到逃离现状的目的，即，民主基本失败，法治的结果却是权力无限扩张，底层阶级跨越难如登天，中产日夜担忧自己和后代如何呆在中产。他们需要的是催眠药和麻醉剂——或者从另一个角度来看，是毒品——而在这个方面，近代以来中国没有人能比得上毛泽东。", "timestamp": 1649513142}}